cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is about end-to-end automatic speech recognition, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and speech processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves training neural networks, which could fall under cs.SD (Sound). Additionally, the paper proposes a practical training scheme, which could be related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves information fusion, which could be related to signal processing (cs.SI).
